---
description: Taste and design rules for AI API Ops.
globs: src/components/**,src/pages/**,src/data/**
alwaysApply: false
---

- Preserve A · Ops Terminal visual identity.
- Do not redesign the site unless explicitly asked.
- Keep dark developer ops feel.
- Keep terminal / ops snapshot style.
- Keep H1 dominant and hero uncrowded.
- Do not turn homepage into generic SaaS landing page.
- Do not add fake dashboards, noisy charts, purple gradients, stock images or heavy animations.
- Do not change global color tokens or spacing scale without explicit approval.
- Any homepage copy expansion must pass taste check: no crowded first screen, no keyword stuffing above the fold.
